<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>117</hymn_number>
<author>Thangngur</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lalpa, Na min zahum hen la,
 Na gam chu lopi takin hung tung hen;
 Enin Na gam chu sukneu guon,
 Lei thuneihna suolin a mang;
 Na sakmin hun chawisang kitin.

[V2]
 Aw Isu ka Hukdampa,
 Na min hun chawisangin;
 Phaicham pak lili khawtang ngui a hin,
 Suolna nuoisieh dingin hung pak lun in,

[V3]
 2. Gingte laka gitloh um hin,
 I Lalpau min thimthu sie'n alel hi;
 A minsiet ding I phal dingum?
 A melsiet ding I tiem dingum?
 I thagau uh damna ahi.

[V4]
 3. Isu'n &quot;Ka min agensiet un,
 Suihlung a na taluoi&quot; A tii;
 A min thiengtho chawisang ding leh,
 A dikna silhpuona nei di'n;
 Tatsa mihing a um puou em?

[V5]
 4. Gitloh na'n taluo a nei puoi,
 Thagau sang-za a puimang zota ie;
 Zuomang vawnchawih thiengtho penle,
 Khawvela a hung lenlai khan;
 Thisan pawtin a matsak hi

[V6]
 Suol vangin muonna um lo,
 Khawvel dahum ahin;
 Van gam ka ngai ie, Ka Pa In nuom khu,
 &quot;Gitloh meipi a zing ta puoi&quot; a tiu.</lyrics>
<title>Aw Isu Ka Hukdampa</title>
</song>